 We did not discuss the issue of the Hawks. It s an act of desperation State institutions are getting into the political terrain. It s dangerous Mantashe said.He said the ruling party was spending more time discussing cohesion and unity within the party .The Sunday Times this week wrote that the investigating unit was investigating the three for failing to report Jonas's sensational claim that one of the Gupta brothers Ajay offered him a R600-million bribe and the finance minister post.Hawks spokesperson Hangwani Mulaudzi denied these allegations saying the investigating unit was not probing any of the three. We are not investigating any of them. The person the Sunday Times spoke to must tell the country what he is talking about Mulaudzi said on Sunday. - TMG Digital